measurements.description: Seventeen flowers and five buds on four up to 24-cm strongly arching inflorescences; flower cream overlaid pale green, heavy burgundy spots on reverse; petals lanceolate, slightly rolled, outer margin deep burgundy spotting; lip side lobes striped burgundy, midlobe overlaid burgundy spots coalesing to stripes, keel pale green; column pale green, anther cap white; substance average; texture matte.
